/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好話佢地日日出嚟俾人屌，CCTVB cut撚晒記者問答，撚有人睇到咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3d3052610b256bd9f0183d4a29865ff43465bb9","tid":1436063,"uid":98842,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0b38cb7f68a7bfd758715dc16abbd86db1bec3c9","tid":1436063,"uid":276273,"like":68,"dislike":2,"score":66,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:10:15.000Z","msg":"咪露出馬腳更多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:34:04.000Z","msg":"【唔該做返主動】我地渣住幾多核彈係手<br />\n <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1435712\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1435712</a><br />\n - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人！把所有銀行存款提走，兌美元現鈔存家中夾萬。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1423812\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1423812</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/09/163005_5871bdc8a2f329da0da5308082ad10bb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F09%2F163005_5871bdc8a2f329da0da5308082ad10bb.png&h=2d49925c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/09/163006_64b6d441a4b05cbbe67745bcf2c10408.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F09%2F163006_64b6d441a4b05cbbe67745bcf2c10408.png&h=15ec3508&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3067fbc3d57de783b5585b42e40bb35aa0a44b7c","tid":1436063,"uid":63461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:34:22.000Z","msg":"唔好理佢"},{"pid":"aae835ab2649e068ef862c4fd865dfd04a68b661","tid":1436063,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d212ae3f2624205f86bdb196acb961a72685393","tid":1436063,"uid":59297,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:33:30.000Z","msg":"大家唔好打晒丁啦<br />\n<br />\n佢日日開記招拎話語權，話香港好亂經濟好差，好撚多人會信、好多人會想快啲過返平靜生活㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />